Articles.Content:
So, I haven't played since .24 was released (July or so) and I decided to get back into KSP after watching the movie Europa Report. I updated all my mods, and double checked that they were updated, but I can't seem to get the game to load. It freezes at seemingly random spots when I try to load and gives me a crash report.

Here's a log link: https://www.dropbox.com/s/x6aaypk0ipz9p51/output_log.txt?dl=0

I'm not sure what else to give in the way of info, as I have no way of knowing which mod is causing this issue.
